", "topics": 366, "footer": null, "header": "终身学习", "title_alternative": "Education", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/0690/59b7/126_mini.png?m=1371465007", "stars": 75, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 126, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 612745, "username": "shrimpDumpling", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/shrimpDumpling", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c08/e5bf/612745_mini.png?m=1744704596", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c08/e5bf/612745_normal.png?m=1744704596", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c08/e5bf/612745_large.png?m=1744704596", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c08/e5bf/612745_xlarge.png?m=1744704596", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8c08/e5bf/612745_xlarge.png?m=1744704596", "created": 1675752395, "last_modified": 1744704596}, "last_reply_by": "luwies", "last_touched": 1749616009, "title": "高考完被送去小工厂干两个月，是我这辈子做过最无意义的事", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1137675", "created": 1749544923, "deleted": 0, "content": "17 年高考完，被父母逼着出去找暑假工，美名其曰体验挣钱的不容易，\r\n可能他们也是好心，但是老一辈的人只有苦难教育、棍棒教育，\r\n也没有人脉和认知介绍真正能提升能力的实习机会，\r\n每天骑一个小时单车跑去工厂折纸盒，\r\n如果说有什么体会，那就是如果一天要坐 12 小时，至少要给胶凳垫个坐垫。\r\n\r\n两个月的工资最后也用来交学费，住宿费，和开学后的生活费了。\r\n\r\n18 岁后受苦的机会可太多了，可连续 3 个月的假期几乎没有，\r\n无非就是想让我知道要好好读书以后不要在底层打工，\r\n\r\n可是家境、职业选择、人脉、认知都在死读书之上，\r\n选择比努力更重要，\r\n如果现在失业吃不起饭了，我还是得去送外卖，那两个月的打工对我来说毫无意义。", "content_rendered": "<p>17 年高考完，被父母逼着出去找暑假工，美名其曰体验挣钱的不容易，\n可能他们也是好心，但是老一辈的人只有苦难教育、棍棒教育，\n也没有人脉和认知介绍真正能提升能力的实习机会，\n每天骑一个小时单车跑去工厂折纸盒，\n如果说有什么体会，那就是如果一天要坐 12 小时，至少要给胶凳垫个坐垫。</p>\n<p>两个月的工资最后也用来交学费，住宿费，和开学后的生活费了。</p>\n<p>18 岁后受苦的机会可太多了，可连续 3 个月的假期几乎没有，\n无非就是想让我知道要好好读书以后不要在底层打工，</p>\n<p>可是家境、职业选择、人脉、认知都在死读书之上，\n选择比努力更重要，\n如果现在失业吃不起饭了，我还是得去送外卖，那两个月的打工对我来说毫无意义。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1749544923, "replies": 114, "id": 1137675}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 28825, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3178, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 432093, "username": "WilsonGGG", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/WilsonGGG", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_mini.png?m=1739944035", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_normal.png?m=1739944035", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_large.png?m=1739944035", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_xlarge.png?m=1739944035", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_xlarge.png?m=1739944035", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7771/e159/432093_xlarge.png?m=1739944035", "created": 1564104554, "last_modified": 1739944035}, "last_reply_by": "azukipanda", "last_touched": 1749618135, "title": "Liquid Glass：时代的列车不可阻挡", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1137650", "created": 1749540732, "deleted": 0, "content": "时代的列车不可阻挡\r\n\r\n网络放大了我们作为人类的两个特质：\r\n1. 抗拒变化\r\n2. 喜欢在早期根据自己无来由的直觉下结论（包括本水贴）\r\n\r\n在 iOS 7 从拟物化切换到扁平化的时候，无数“先贤”就发出过和今天大家一样的评论（请看 VCR： https://v2ex.com/t/71945 ），但扁平化的浪潮奔腾了 12 年还未停歇。\r\n\r\niOS 26 Beta 1 我更新了，有很多 BUG 、卡顿、设计不合理，但我觉得大方向还是逻辑的，不能用迭代了长达 12 年的成熟设计语言来对比这个 beta 1 版本的新时代。\r\n\r\n另外一点感叹：我们大部分人自以为在某个时间点发出了什么高论（包括本水贴），其实翻阅 2013 年关于 iOS 7 的很多帖子，都是一样的屁话，但时代的列车不可阻挡，苹果成功把 iOS 7 的列车开到了今天，Liquid Glass 能走到哪里，以后才知道。", "content_rendered": "时代的列车不可阻挡<br /><br />网络放大了我们作为人类的两个特质：<br />1. 抗拒变化<br />2. 喜欢在早期根据自己无来由的直觉下结论（包括本水贴）<br /><br />在 iOS 7 从拟物化切换到扁平化的时候，无数“先贤”就发出过和今天大家一样的评论（请看 VCR： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/71945\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://v2ex.com/t/71945</a> ），但扁平化的浪潮奔腾了 12 年还未停歇。<br /><br />iOS 26 Beta 1 我更新了，有很多 BUG 、卡顿、设计不合理，但我觉得大方向还是逻辑的，不能用迭代了长达 12 年的成熟设计语言来对比这个 beta 1 版本的新时代。<br /><br />另外一点感叹：我们大部分人自以为在某个时间点发出了什么高论（包括本水贴），其实翻阅 2013 年关于 iOS 7 的很多帖子，都是一样的屁话，但时代的列车不可阻挡，苹果成功把 iOS 7 的列车开到了今天，Liquid Glass 能走到哪里，以后才知道。", "last_modified": 1749540732, "replies": 111, "id": 1137650}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 8092, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 1859, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 673397, "username": "5261", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/5261", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/35f3bd2ff78daccfd497fffe69c40dce?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/35f3bd2ff78daccfd497fffe69c40dce?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/35f3bd2ff78daccfd497fffe69c40dce?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1706251353, "last_modified": 1747183875}, "last_reply_by": "lasuar", "last_touched": 1749612041, "title": "老父亲有高血压，爱喝酒，死活不愿意吃降压药，怎么破？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1137636", "created": 1749538393, "deleted": 0, "content": "去年老父亲体检的时候说自己有高血压，但是日常没啥反应，他就不愿意吃降压药\r\n\r\n不管我过年的时候怎么劝，怎么提示高血压的风险，就是听不进去，不知道咋破了\r\n\r\n我估计老父亲是担心吃药后就不能喝酒啥的，舍不得", "content_rendered": "<p>去年老父亲体检的时候说自己有高血压，但是日常没啥反应，他就不愿意吃降压药</p>\n<p>不管我过年的时候怎么劝，怎么提示高血压的风险，就是听不进去，不知道咋破了</p>\n<p>我估计老父亲是担心吃药后就不能喝酒啥的，舍不得</p>\n", "last_modified": 1749602877, "replies": 79, "id": 1137636}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 28825, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3178, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 640023, "username": "Lowlife", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lowlife", "website": "i.hm", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4728eb97f78b8e8b8b2714364c7642b7?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4728eb97f78b8e8b8b2714364c7642b7?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4728eb97f78b8e8b8b2714364c7642b7?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1690252763, "last_modified": 1690252763}, "last_reply_by": "iyaozhen", "last_touched": 1749617947, "title": "iPhone 恶心的液态玻璃 ui 会不会被国内安卓跟风？毕竟刘海屏这种恶心的东西都被抄过了。🤢", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1137624", "created": 1749536501, "deleted": 0, "content": "Apple 怎么做出来这种丑东西🤢", "content_rendered": "<p>Apple 怎么做出来这种丑东西🤢</p>\n", "last_modified": 1749536501, "replies": 68, "id": 1137624}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1739135407", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1739135407", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 230